OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly dry with sunny spells on
OL,6,FMonday morning. Cloud thickening early
OL,7,Fafternoon, with outbreaks of mostly
OL,8,Flight rain spreading east. Still
OL,9,Frather breezy but mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,12,Fmostly light rain this evening, but
OL,13,Frain slowly easing to become largely
OL,14,Fdry by dawn. Wind easing. Mild.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FMostly dry Tuesday morning
OL,17,Fand often cloudy, but some brighter
OL,18,Fspells are possible. Cloud clearing in
OL,19,Fthe afternoon to give longer sunny
OL,20,Fspells. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
